{"tid":1048523,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"新vr頭盔上手","createTime":"2019-03-05T17:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T07:56:20.000Z","uid":28563,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"26f9446606ec6530006fc335536657663c0322af","tid":1048523,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:08:22.000Z","msg":"pimax 5k<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/06/005908_0cec7cb2a72a41a86480771ae15a958a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2F005908_0cec7cb2a72a41a86480771ae15a958a.jpeg&h=30a04437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比htc vive<br />\n+ 視野 好 撚 大，兩隻眼9成位cover晒，係鼻果個位差d<br />\n+ 行rgb lcd，冇粒粒，電腦頂到既話清到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n- 色水<br />\n- 黑位<br />\n(我應該買5k be，但要睇粒粒mon)<br />\n- 邊位扭曲，雖然軟件未來搞得掂<br />\n- pitool唔係好掂<br />\n- 手掣有時甩tracking，vive冇事，唔知steamvr問題定usb問題，reddit見有少少人同我一樣。用vive linkbox中轉usb感覺上好d，但仍會出事。希望之後fix到<br />\n- 線短過vive，我要買dp+usb extender<br />\n- 單眼4k x 3k，甚至6k x 4k，2080ti都收皮，但呢個唔係個headset既問題<br />\n- 戴起上黎冇vive咁舒服，雖然可以第3方<br />\n- 冇無線，下年出唔出到都成問題<br />\n<br />\n總計 7/10，過一排軟件ok貨源充足配套有齊可以考慮"},{"pid":"4ed29f1e3907d1307a534359f261cea6c4bb45cd","tid":1048523,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"會唔會頭暈"},{"pid":"16f1978d0bffb7121fd53d5b1d7e109ba7c7b23a","tid":1048523,"uid":138724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似幾抵屌"},{"pid":"dfb3ac63c7c2a3c1714aaeaa1f957d15144869c1","tid":1048523,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"唔買8k?"},{"pid":"e4c9dbb58d52f005e828b47e4ab198ee23934f32","tid":1048523,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ed29f1e3907d1307a534359f261cea6c4bb45cd","tid":1048523,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"會唔會頭暈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"呢款頭盔個視距好難較得岩，戴唔岩/較唔岩有機會眼殘<br />\n<br />\n頭盔就好大機會唔會，電腦vr幾時都keep到90fps，擰頭係即刻比到反應，隻game drop fps唔會定住&hellip;但如果隻game fps唔足90就睇你體質啦<br />\n<br />\n我就兩款頭盔都唔會，但手機vr唔係好掂"},{"pid":"13a8a55cb2f6c1e669a3cae8f96e14ca0815b66e","tid":1048523,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"16f1978d0bffb7121fd53d5b1d7e109ba7c7b23a","tid":1048523,"uid":138724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似幾抵屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"你本身冇htc vive唔建議買，699 usd係淨headset"},{"pid":"23925410a7a4ffb92be1278724bfb3de83a32796","tid":1048523,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfb3ac63c7c2a3c1714aaeaa1f957d15144869c1","tid":1048523,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"唔買8k?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"8k係2560*1440 upscale上3840*2160既pentile粒粒lcd mon，見到都唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e999ff9da02c43d6ad3e5f7c08475996cf78630","tid":1048523,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:50:28.000Z","msg":"恰恰order左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會鏡頭易濛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f316dcb088a6da213fbca9557a827921a23b75","tid":1048523,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e999ff9da02c43d6ad3